title: ELIZABETHTOWN - [ENG][2005] - LIBRE & VERITAS
description: Elizabethtown is a 2005 American film written and directed by Cameron Crowe starring Orlando Bloom and Kirsten Dunst. Orlando Bloom plays a shoe designer visiting his father&#039;s hometown in Kentucky in the days following the father&#039;s death, and Kirsten Dunst plays a flight attendant. Alec Baldwin has a small role as a CEO of an athletic shoe company, and Susan Sarandon appears as a grieving widow.
